data.description: Enjoy the Florida lifestyle in this updated jewel in North Andrews Gardens. This home was charmingly transformed by the proud owners. The home boasts plenty of updates throughout. The Roof and Impact Windows and Doors were replaced in 2021. AC was replaced in 2020. You'll find gleaming terrazzo flooring throughout. Enjoy a spacious primary bedroom with sliding doors leading you out to the serene garden. A Stylish kitchen redone in 2021. A Chic bathroom, recently updated. There is sizable separate laundry room attached. This could be the perfect starter home or ideal second home. There is a large garden with room for a pool. Close to downtown Ferdale, shopping, dining and the fabulous Beaches. Make it yours today!
